  "detailed_description": "\"monoch room\" is an adventure game with some puzzle elements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077200/extras/c1a43405345424c087dd9e2736fd42de.avif?t=1768174839\" width=616 height=158 /></span><br><br>◆ Story<br><br>I was exhausted with everything.<br>After losing consciousness, I found myself in a strange room without knowing how I got there.<br><br>Someone unknown led me deeper into the room.<br><br>\"I thought you would come this far.\"<br><br>Eventually, I saw a past that I had forgotten.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077200/extras/2d77e2b498aa74841059c84fea63b998.avif?t=1768174839\" width=616 height=158 /></span><br><br>◆ Game Features<br><br>    A walking simulator where various events happen as you walk.<br>    Progress through the story by examining objects.<br>    No quest markers or time limits, allowing for relaxed gameplay.<br>    Puzzles are simple.<br><br>Playtime: 10 to 30 minutes<br><br>◆ Video Streaming Guidelines<br><br>    Streaming is permitted without the need for permission, for both individuals and businesses.",
